review_blob: On tap at DFH Rehoboth.  While definitely more boozy than hoppy, this is still a well balanced beer with a lot of complexity...just dont expect an IPA.
I personally cant stand this beer...boozy, vanilla air-freshener meets sweet cough syrup.  A lot going on for sure...but none of it appealing to my taste.
beer_name: Tregs The Mad Elf Holiday Ale

review_blob: This is one of my favorite beers.  The oak combines with the strong hop character and malty sweetness beautifully.
